    ],
    "text": "The 4th Accused-Appellant-Petitioner-Petitioner has filed a revision application in this court seeking to set aside the order made on 29.03.2019, by the Learned High Court Judge of Panadura, refusing to enlarge the 4th Accused- Appellant-Petitioner-Petitioner on Bail Pending Appeal.",
